name: Gift Wrapping
description:
Buying a gift?

This option of gift wrap gives a little extra to that special someone.

All items are nestled in acid free tissue paper snug in a clear circular tube or clear cubed box picked especially for the size and shape to ensure best protection and best presentation.

* Seasonal is for orders placed around Christmas, Easter, Halloween, St Patrick's Day etc and will have the appropriate wrapping

* It's a birthday is for orders when buying for a birthday (if they have a favourite colour let us know at checkout and we will try and wrap for them)

Gifts and samples are still sent with the appropriate order amounts - please select male or female so we can best tailor these if not unisex.
See our FAQ for more on this if you are unsure.

All these gifted orders will be sent in our signature black envelopes/mail boxes and will not include a price on the invoice.

** If you would prefer not to have an invoice sent at all (this means there will be no list of the items in the order) please mention it at checkout. **

name: Stargazer Hair Colour
description: A semi-permanent hair colour with conditioner for direct application to the hair. Free of ammonia or peroxide stargazer hair colour allows you to achieve a wide range of vibrant translucent colours. Stargazer hair colour can be applied to natural, dyed or bleached hair. For best results use on pre-lightened hair. (Please note that stargazer hair colour will not cover white or grey hair). All 26 of the stargazer hair colours can be mixed together to produce an ever wider array of colours. The inside of the hair colour box contains instructions and caution note in eight different languages. A pair of disposable gloves are included for use with the hair dye. ** If the product you are looking for is not listed as available please contact us as products are always available on application **

Kit contains:

Plastic Gloves

Dust Free Bleach Powder

Creme Developer

Mixing Tub

Plastic Cap




Remember to shampoo out all the FLASHLIGHTNING from your hair thoroughly before you apply MANIC PANIC (or any other) Hair Colour. Leftover bleach residue on the hair can prevent the hair colour from processing properly

 
BLEACH RESULTS ARE PERMANENT


Please read all instructions and perform strand test before using FLASHLIGHTNING
